# YAAT Architecture Diagram

## High-Level Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "CLI Layer"
        A[main.rs<br/>Entry Point]
        B[cli.rs<br/>clap - CLI Parser]
    end

    subgraph "Command Layer"
        C1[commands/init.rs<br/>Initialize Repo]
        C2[commands/add.rs<br/>Add Files]
        C3[commands/sync.rs<br/>Sync to System]
        C4[commands/backup.rs<br/>Backup to Repo]
        C5[commands/status.rs<br/>Show Status]
    end

    subgraph "Core Modules"
        M1[config.rs<br/>YAML Configuration]
        M2[git.rs<br/>Git Operations<br/>git2 crate]
        M3[platform.rs<br/>Cross-platform Paths<br/>dirs crate]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        E1[clap v4.5<br/>CLI Arguments]
        E2[git2 v0.20<br/>libgit2 bindings]
        E3[dirs v6.0<br/>Standard directories]
        E4[serde + serde_yaml<br/>Config serialization]
        E5[tracing + subscriber<br/>Logging]
        E6[anyhow<br/>Error handling]
    end

    subgraph "System Layer"
        S1[Filesystem<br/>~/.config, ~]
        S2[Git Repository<br/>~/.dotfiles]
        S3[Symlinks<br/>or Copies]
    end

    A --> B
    B --> C1
    B --> C2
    B --> C3
    B --> C4
    B --> C5

    C1 --> M1
    C1 --> M2
    C2 --> M2
    C2 --> M3
    C3 --> M1
    C3 --> M2
    C3 --> M3
    C4 --> M1
    C4 --> M2
    C4 --> M3
    C5 --> M1
    C5 --> M2

    M1 -.-> E4
    M2 -.-> E2
    M3 -.-> E3

    M2 --> S1
    M2 --> S2
    M3 --> S1
    C3 --> S3
```

## Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as CLI Parser<br/>(clap)
    participant Cmd as Command Handler
    participant Config as Config<br/>(yaat.yaml)
    participant Git as Git<br/>(git2)
    participant Platform as Platform<br/>(dirs)
    participant FS as Filesystem

    User->>CLI: yaat init
    CLI->>Cmd: Parse & Dispatch
    Cmd->>Git: GitRepo::init()
    Git->>FS: Create .dotfiles/
    Git->>FS: Create config/, home/, hosts/
    Git->>FS: Create .gitignore
    Cmd->>Config: Write yaat.yaml
    Git->>FS: Initial commit

    User->>CLI: yaat add ~/.config/kitty/kitty.conf
    CLI->>Cmd: Parse & Dispatch
    Cmd->>Platform: config_dir() → ~/.config
    Cmd->>Platform: system_to_repo_path()
    Cmd->>FS: Copy file to repo
    Cmd->>Git: repo.add()
    Cmd->>Git: repo.commit()

    User->>CLI: yaat sync
    CLI->>Cmd: Parse & Dispatch
    Cmd->>Config: Load yaat.yaml
    Cmd->>Platform: Get hostname
    Cmd->>Git: Scan repo files
    loop For each file
        Cmd->>Platform: repo_to_system_path()
        Cmd->>FS: Check if exists
        Cmd->>FS: Backup existing
        Cmd->>FS: Create symlink
    end

    User->>CLI: yaat status
    CLI->>Cmd: Parse & Dispatch
    Cmd->>Git: repo.status()
    Cmd->>Config: Load config
    Cmd->>FS: Check sync state
```

