## Command Flow

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    
    Idle --> Parsing: User Input
    Parsing --> Init: "yaat init"
    Parsing --> Add: "yaat add"
    Parsing --> Sync: "yaat sync"
    Parsing --> Backup: "yaat backup"
    Parsing --> Status: "yaat status"
    
    Init --> GitInit: Create repo
    GitInit --> ConfigWrite: Write yaat.yaml
    ConfigWrite --> Done: Commit
    
    Add --> ValidatePath: Check file
    ValidatePath --> CopyFile: Copy to repo
    CopyFile --> GitAdd: Stage
    GitAdd --> Done: Commit
    
    Sync --> LoadConfig: Read config
    LoadConfig --> ScanRepo: Find files
    ScanRepo --> CheckSystem: File exists?
    CheckSystem --> Backup: Yes
    CheckSystem --> CreateSymlink: No
    Backup --> CreateSymlink
    CreateSymlink --> Done
    
    Backup --> LoadConfig2: Read config
    LoadConfig2 --> ScanSystem: Find configs
    ScanSystem --> CopyBack: Copy to repo
    CopyBack --> GitCommit: Stage & commit
    GitCommit --> Done
    
    Status --> LoadConfig3: Read config
    LoadConfig3 --> GitStatus: Check repo
    GitStatus --> Compare: Compare with system
    Compare --> Done
    
    Done --> Idle: Return to shell
```

